🏛️ Design Decisions
Decision	Rationale
Raw + Processed Data Separation	Allows feature reprocessing without losing original data
Server-side Feature Extraction	Ensures consistent calculation across all clients
JWT Authentication	Stateless, scalable authentication
Prisma ORM	Type-safe database operations
CSV Export	Universal format for all ML tools
React + Vite	Fast development, optimal builds
🚧 Future Improvements
Digraph/Trigraph Analysis - Time between specific key pairs

Train/Test Split Endpoint - Automatic dataset partitioning

Model Inference API - Real-time authentication

Continuous Authentication - Monitor during entire session

Anomaly Detection - Identify unusual typing patterns

Feature Normalization - Standardized ML input

Visualization Dashboard - Typing pattern graphs

Multi-language Support - Different keyboard layouts

